{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "screens-playlists-api",
		"name": "Screens & Playlists API",
		"description": "API collection for Screens & Playlists System",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"token\", jsonData.token);",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"userId\", jsonData.user.id);",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"userRole\", jsonData.user.role);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"auth",
								"login"
							]
						},
						"description": "Login with email and password. Returns JWT token.\n\n**Seeded Users:**\n- Admin: admin@example.com / admin123\n- Editor: editor@example.com / editor123"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Signup",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"token\", jsonData.token);",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"userId\", jsonData.user.id);",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"userRole\", jsonData.user.role);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"newuser@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\",\n    \"role\": \"EDITOR\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/signup",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"auth",
								"signup"
							]
						},
						"description": "Create a new user account.\n\n**Request Body:**\n```json\n{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\" (required),\n  \"password\": \"password123\" (required, min 6 characters),\n  \"role\": \"ADMIN\" | \"EDITOR\" (required)\n}\n```\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"token\": \"jwt-token\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": \"...\",\n    \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n    \"role\": \"EDITOR\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Errors:**\n- `USER_ALREADY_EXISTS`: Email already registered\n- `INVALID_INPUT`: Validation errors"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
		{
