						"description": "Get paginated list of screens with optional search.\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- `search` (optional): Search term for screen name (case-insensitive)\n- `page` (optional): Page number (default: 1)\n- `limit` (optional): Items per page (default: 10)\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"items\": [...],\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"page\": 1,\n  \"limit\": 10\n}\n```"
					},
					"response": []
